Umubare w'abarwaye Coronavirus (COVID-19) ugaragaza ingendo zisa n'izo mu bihugu bya EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza, bikaba byemeza ko nubwo icyiciro gitandukana bitewe n'igihugu, icyorezo cya COVID-19 kirushaho kwiyongera mu bihugu byose.
Dukurikije ibyabaye mu Butaliyani, ibihugu, ibitaro n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi bunonosoye bigomba kurushaho kwitegura kongera umubare w'abarwayi ba COVID-19 bazajya bakeneye kwitabwaho mu by'ubuzima, cyane cyane ubuvuzi bunonosoye.
Ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza 2019, hari inkuru z'abantu benshi barwaye indwara y'ubuhumekero bw'amaraso ku mpamvu zitazwi mu mujyi wa Wuhan, mu ntara ya Hubei, mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 9 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo cy'Ubushinwa gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara cyatangaje ko icyateye ari virusi nshya ya Coronavirusi ubu izwi nka Coronavirusi 2 ifitanye isano n'indwara yo guhumeka ifite ubukana (SARS-CoV-2).
Kuva icyo gihe, indwara yatewe n'icyorezo cya SARS-CoV-2 yise indwara ya Coronavirus (COVID-19).
Kugeza ubu hari ibimenyetso bigaragaza ko hafi 80% by'abantu banduye COVID-19 bafite uburwayi bworoheje; ni ukuvuga ko bafite ubwandu bw'imyenda yo mu mpumuro, bafite ibimenyetso cyangwa badafite, kandi abenshi muri bo bakira.
Mu bantu bagera kuri 14%, COVID-19 yagabanyije uburwayi bukabije bukenera kuba mu bitaro, mu gihe abandi 6% baba bafite uburwayi bukomeye bukenera kwitabwaho cyane.
Umubare w'abapfuye mu barwayi bari mu bitaro kubera COVID-19 wari ugera kuri 4%.
Muri iki cyifuzo, tugereranya imibare y'abantu banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu byose byo mu muryango w'ubumwe bw'u Burayi, mu karere k'ubukungu bw'u Burayi, mu Bwongereza no mu Bushinwa, n'ibyabaye mu ntara ya Hubei.
Nanone, turagereranya umubare w'abanduye COVID-19 muri EU/EEA n'Ubwongereza n'uw'u Butaliyani hagati ya 31 Mutarama na 15 Werurwe 2020.
