Virusi za Corona zisanzwe zatumaga abantu barwara indwara zidakomeye, zikaba ari zo zituma abantu bagera kuri 15% bahura n'ibicurane bine bikunze kubaho.
Nyamara muri iki kinyejana, twahuye na virusi ya Corona iteza indwara zikomeye mu bantu inshuro ebyiri, SARS-CoV na MERS-CoV, zatumye iyi ndwara yibasira mu Bushinwa mu 2003 no muri Arabiya Sawudite mu 2012, kandi vuba aha iyi ndwara yageze mu bindi bihugu byinshi ku gipimo cy'ubwandu n'urupfu bibabaje.
Bityo, COVID-19 iriho ubu ni icyorezo cya gatatu cya Coronavirus mu mateka y'abantu.
Nkuko bigaragara mu ishusho ya 1.1, amatsinda y'abantu bafite ubwandu bw'ibihaha bitazwi bwavuye i Wuhan yatangijwe ku wa 31 Ukuboza 2019 na Komisiyo y'Ubuzima y'Igihugu y'u Bushinwa.
Nyuma y'iminsi irindwi, icyorezo cya Coronavirus cyasohotse.
Ku itariki ya 15 Mutarama 2020, Wuhan yatangaje ko hari umuntu wa mbere wapfuye.
Hagati aho, iki cyorezo cyakwirakwiriye mu migi, intara n'ibihugu by'abaturanyi.
Ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama, habayeho ubwandu mu bakozi b'ubuvuzi, ibyo bikaba bigaragaza ko indwara ishobora guhitana umuntu umwe.
Ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama, umujyi wa Wuhan warafunze, imodoka zose za rusange zihagarikwa.
Ku itariki ya 24 Mutarama, ubushakashatsi bwa mbere bwakozwe ku ndwara bwagaragaje ko mu bantu 41 bari bamaze kwandura, 21 gusa ari bo bari bafite ikoranabuhanga ryihariye n'isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Wuhan, aho indwara yatangiriye mu nyamaswa zitazwi.
Ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama, Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryatangaje ko iki cyorezo ari imimerere y'ivutuza isi yose.
Igihe iyi raporo yasohokaga, icyo cyorezo cyari kimaze gukwirakwira mu Bushinwa hose no mu bindi bihugu bigera kuri 50 ku isi hose (Igishushanyo (Igishushanyo 2) 2.
Uko ibintu bigenda byihuta, icyorezo kigomba kuba gifite aho gihera n'ubukana bwacyo.
