SARS-CoV-2 ishobora no gukora poroteyine ngufi y'ubushakashatsi ihimbwe na orf3b n'imiterere y'ubushakashatsi ihimbwe na orf8.
orf3b muri SARS-CoV-2 ishobora kugira uruhare mu ndwara z'umugera wa virusi kandi igabanya imvugo ya IFNβ; ariko, orf8 nta rwego cyangwa uburyo ifite akazi kazwi.
Ku ya 18 Gashyantare 2020, Chu n'abandi batangaje ko ingirabuzima fatizo ya angiotensin 2 y'umuntu ifite uburebure buhagije mu gihe ikoranabuhanga ry'ubushakashatsi rigenda ryihuta cyane, rifite ubuhanga bwa 2.9 Å mu gice gifite icyitwa B0AT1.
