Ubucuruzi bwo muri Ositaraliya bugabanya umubare w'amapapuro y'icyumba cyo kuvuramo
Imiduga ibiri yo muri Australia ya Wallworth & Co. ku mugoroba wo ku wa gatandatu no ku cyumweru, yashimangiye ko igiciro cy'ibitabo by'amazu y'isuku cyagabanutseho ku byiciro bibiri by'amazu ya Wallworth & Co. no ku byiciro kimwe by'amazu ya Co. Co. ku rwego rw'ishami ku rwego rw'igihugu.
Nk'uko navuze, amaduka ya Aldi yari afite umwenda umwe, ari wo kuwa mbere.
Aya mategeko yo kugura yashyizwe ahagaragara nk'amabaruwa ku mbuga z'amafaranga mu maduka no ku rubuga rwa Facebook.
Hari amakuru avuga ko abaguzi batangiye kubitunga kubera impungenge z'icyorezo cya COVID-19 mu gihe abantu baba bakeneye kwigunga.
Ku wa gatatu amaduka ya Wall-Worthes yemeje ko hari ibipimo by'ibitabo by'ubwiherero by'amazu byemewe kugira ngo buri cyemezo cy'igiciro cy'ibyo umuntu yagura kibe kimwe.
Ibi bihinduka nyuma y'ibihano by'ubucuruzi byemejwe n'ibigo bya Wallworth ku itariki ya 4 Werurwe na Coles ku itariki ya 5 Werurwe, byemerera kugura imyenda ine gusa kuri buri gikorwa.
Ubucuruzi bwa Coles bwatangaje mu itangazo ryasohowe ku wa 8 Werurwe ko nubwo hashyizweho amategeko agenga imyenda ine, "ubucuruzi bwinshi bukomeje kugurisha ibyo bafite byose mu isaha imwe yo kubwakira", kandi ko gusaba ari "ibitari byigeze biba", ndetse n'ubucuruzi bwa Aldi bwatangaje ko "bitari byitezwe" mu nyandiko kuri Facebook kuwa kabiri.
Ibicuruzwa byongereye cyane mu cyumweru gishize, nk'uko bivugwa n'umuvugizi wa Wall Worth Stores.
Ubucuruzi bwa Costco i Canberra mu cyumweru gishize bwavuze ko amafaranga yemerewe kugurwa ari amafaranga abiri.
Kugira ngo ibyo bigabanuke, ibigo bya Coles byasabye ababitanga amafaranga menshi no kongera umuvuduko wo gutanga, kandi ibigo bya Wallworth byasabye indi mitungo, mu gihe ibigo bya Aldi byatanze imitungo yabyo mu gihe cy'ibitaramo by'umwiherero byari biteganyijwe kuwa gatatu kare.
Russell Zimmerman, umuyobozi mukuru w'ishyirahamwe ry'abacuruzi bo muri Ositaraliya, yavuze ko abacuruzi bagerageza kongera ibicuruzwa, ariko ko amategeko y'inama y'akarere ku gihe cy'itangwa ry'amakamyo atuma ibintu birushaho kugorana.
Ibiza by'iterambere bizaba biri hejuru, aho abaguzi bazajya bagerageza guhangana n'ibisabwa, naho ibicuruzwa by'umwihariko bizaba ari bike.
Ku wa kabiri, amaduka ya Aldi yatangaje ko kubera ko ibicuruzwa byabonekaga hakiri kare, amaduka amwe n'amwe atashoboraga gutanga ibitaramo byo ku wa Gatatu.
Dr. Gary Mortimer, umuhanga mu by'ubucuruzi muri Queensland University of Technology, mu cyegeranyo cye kuri News.com.au, yavuze ko amaduka yuzuye amazu y'ubucuruzi buri joro.
Yavuze ko impapuro z'icyumba cyo mu bwiherero ari ibintu binini cyane, bigatuma umubare w'ibikoresho ugabanuka, kandi iyo bigurishijwe byose, bigasiga ahantu henshi ku mashelufu, bigatuma umuntu yumva afite ikibazo cy'ibura.
