Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ritangaza ko COVID-19 ari icyorezo cy'indwara
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (WHO) ryatangaje kuri uyu wa Gatatu ko icyorezo cya COVID-19 - icyorezo cyatewe na virusi ya Corona gifitanye isano n'indwara yo mu mutwe (SRS) - cyiswe SARS-CoV-2 - cyakomeje kwiyongera.
Nubwo ijambo "icyorezo" ryerekeza gusa ku rugero rw'icyorezo, aho kwerekeza ku muvuduko w'ibyago by'indwara runaka, OMS yavuze ko ari ngombwa gushishikariza ubutegetsi gufata ingamba zikenewe:
"Ibihugu byose biracyabasha guhindura icyorezo.
Umuyobozi mukuru w'umuryango w'abibumbye wita ku buzima, Tedros Adhanom Ghiberisose, yagize ati "iyo ibihugu byiboneye, bigenzura abantu, bikabitaho, bikabarinda, bikabakurikira, bikabatera guhangana".
"Twese dufite impungenge z'uko ibipimo by'ubwirakabiri n'ibyago by'ubwandu ari ibintu biteye ubwoba, ndetse n'uko ibintu byahindutse".
Nk'uko Dr. Tom Friedan, wahoze ari umuyobozi w'Ikigo cyo kurwanya no gukumira indwara muri Amerika abivuga, iki cyorezo "cyari kitigeze kibaho".
Mu itangazo CNN yashyize ahagaragara muri Gashyantare, yagize ati "nta wundi virusi yo mu myanya y'ubuhumekero yakurikiranwe kuva yatangira gukwirakwira kugeza ku isi hose, uretse icyorezo cya grippe".
Ibinyuranye n'ibyo, Gipresso yagize ati "nta ndwara y'icyorezo cya Coronavirus yigeze itugeraho".
Yakomeje agira ati "Nta ndwara na rimwe twabonye ishobora gutegekwa icyarimwe".
Iyo ndwara nshya ivugwaho kuba ari icyorezo nyuma y'icyemezo cya OMS cyo muri Mutarama cyatangaje ko icyorezo cy'indwara ya leta ari ihungabana rihangayikishije isi yose.
Umuyobozi w'Ikigo cy'Igihugu gishinzwe Indwara z'ubwandu n'ubwandu muri Amerika, Dr. Anthony Fawcett, yavuze ibirebana n'iki cyorezo agira ati "kugira ngo ibintu birusheho kuzamba, ni ngombwa ko tuvuga ko bigenda birushaho kuzamba".
Ikigo cy'itangazamakuru cya Associated Press cyatangaje ko ku isi hose hari nibura abantu 126,000 banduye COVID-19 kuva kuwa kane, ndetse hapfa abantu barenga 4600.
Icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019-20 ni icyorezo kirimo kuba cyatewe n'icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019 (COVID-19), cyatewe na Coronavirus 2 ifitanye isano n'indwara yo guhumeka ifite ubukana bukabije (SARS Cove-2).
Icyorezo cy'indwara cyemejwe i Wuhan mu Bushinwa, mu Ukuboza 2019, cyatangajwe nk'ihungabana ry'ubuzima rusange rifite impungenge mpuzamahanga ku wa 30 Mutarama 2020, cyemezwa ko ari icyorezo ku wa 11 Werurwe 2020.
Ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 1.61 banduye COVID-19 mu bihugu 210 n'uturere, bituma abantu bagera ku 97.000 bapfa.
Abantu bagera ku 364.000 barakize.
Mu Bushinwa, umubare w'abapfa ugereranywa na 4%, mu gihe ku isi hose uri hagati ya 13.04% muri Aljeriya na 0.08% muri Nouvelle-Zélande.
Ibimenyetso bikunze kugaragara ni umuriro, gusogongera no guhumeka nabi.
Ibibazo by'indwara bishobora kuba ari uburwayi bw'amahaha n'indwara yo guhumeka cyane.
Igihe hagati yo kwanduzwa n'ibimenyetso ubusanzwe kiba iminsi igera kuri itanu, ariko gishobora kuba hagati y'iminsi ibiri n'iminsi 14.
Nta nkingo cyangwa umuti wa virusi bizwi.
Uburyo bw'ibanze bwo kuvura ni ubufasha n'ubufasha mu kugaragaza ibimenyetso. Ibikorwa by'ubudahangarwa byatanzwe birimo gukaraba intoki, guhisha umunwa igihe ushuhije, gukomeza kwihererana, kugenzura no kwiherera ku muntu ukekwaho kuba yaranduye.
Abayobozi ku isi hose bitabira aka kaga bashyizeho amategeko agenga ingendo, ibipimo by'ubuvuzi, kubuza abantu kujya mu bindi bihugu, kugenzura ibyago byo mu kazi no gufunga ibigo.
Iki cyorezo cyatumye habaho imvururu zikomeye ku rwego rw'isi yose mu bukungu no mu mibanire, ibikorwa by'imikino, iby'idini, ibya politiki n'iby'umuco bigatezwa imbere cyangwa bigatwarwa, kandi ikibazo cy'ibura ry'ibikoresho ku buryo bw'ikirenga cyongerewe n'icyifuzo cyo kugura.
