Ubu leta nyinshi zishinzwe gushyiraho cyangwa zisaba ko abantu bakwirinda mu duce twugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Umubare w'abantu bazajya mu materaniro wahanuwe n'inzego za Leta ya Amerika n'imiryango y'ubuzima, wagabanyijwe uhereye ku bantu 250 (niba COVID-19 itaragaragaragarira mu karere) ugera ku bantu 50, nyuma yaho ugera ku bantu 10.
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe 2020, Ubudage bwabujije abantu benshi guteranira hamwe. Abakuze n'abafite indwara z'igihe kirekire nka diyabete, indwara z'umutima, indwara z'ubuhumekero, umuvuduko w'amaraso, intege nke z'imiryango yabo z'ubwirinzi birushaho gutuma barwara indwara zikomeye n'izindi ndwara zikomeye. Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara n'ubudahangarwa cyabateye inama yo kuguma mu rugo igihe cyose bishoboka mu duce tw'indwara hagati y'abaturage. Mu mpera z'ukwezi kwa Werurwe 2020, OMS n'izindi nzego z'ubuzima batangiye gukoresha ijambo "ubutayi bw'imibereho" mu kuvuga "ubutayi bw'umubiri", kugira ngo basobanure ko intego yo kugabanya umubano w'umubiri n'abantu, ari ugukomeza guhuza imibereho myiza, cyangwa kutabana n'abandi.
Gukoresha ijambo "ubutabangane mu by'imibereho" byatumye abantu batangira kwihererana mu by'imibereho aho guterwa inkunga yo gushyikirana n'abandi mu buryo bushya.
Muri ibyo harimo inama yo kudakora imibonano mpuzabitsina uretse n'umuntu ubana na we utanduye cyangwa ufite ibimenyetso byayo.
Abantu bafite COVID-19 n'abakekwaho kuba barwaye, bagirwa inama yo kwiherera mu rugo.
Ibiro by'ubuzima byatanze amabwiriza arambuye yo kwiherera neza. Guverinoma nyinshi zashinze cyangwa zasabye ko abantu bose baba mu duce twibasiwe na cyo bakoresha ibuye ry'ubutabazi.
Amabwiriza akomeye cyane yo kwirinda indwara z'amabuye y'umurava yashyizwe mu bikorwa ku bantu bafite ibyago byinshi.
Abantu bagiranye n'umuntu ufite COVID-19 kandi baherutse kujya mu gihugu cyangwa akarere aho ubwandu bushobora kwiyongera, bagirwa inama yo gukoresha ibuye ry'isuku ry'iminsi 14 mu gihe cy'indi ndwara ishobora kuba.
Uburyo bwo kugabanya icyorezo ni ukugabanya cyangwa guhagarika ikwirakwira ry'icyo cyorezo.
Gufata abantu mu gihe cy'icyorezo ni igikorwa cyo gukurikirana abanduye no kubashyira mu kato, ndetse no gushyiraho izindi ngamba zo kurwanya ubwandu n'inkingo kugira ngo indwara itagenda ikwira abandi bantu.
Iyo kurwanya ikwirakwira ry'indwara bitashoboka, imihati iba ijyanye no kugabanya: hagashyirwaho ingamba zo kugabanya ikwirakwira no kugabanya ingaruka ku rwego rw'ubuzima no ku baturage.
Uburyo bumwe bwo kugabanya ubukana n'ubw'ubundi burashobora gukorwa icyarimwe.
Kugabanya ibiza bisaba gufata ingamba zikomeye zo guhindukiza icyorezo mu kugabanya umubare w'ibanze w'ubwandu ku munsi wa 1. Igice cyo gucunga icyorezo cy'indwara zandura kigerageza kugabanya ikiza cy'icyorezo, mu gihe cyitwa gucururizamo umugogo w'icyorezo.
Ibi bigabanya ibyago byo guhangayika mu buvuzi kandi bigatuma habaho igihe kinini cyo gukora inkingo n'imiti.
Ibitekerezo by'abantu ku giti cyabo, urugero nko kwirinda isuku, kwambara udupfukamunwa n'amabuye y'isuku, harimo ibyo kwirinda indwara; ingamba z'abaturage zigamije gutandukanya abantu ku buryo bw'umubiri, urugero nko gufunga amashuri no guhagarika amateraniro manini; ubufatanye bw'abaturage bwo gutera inkunga abantu kwemera no kwifatanya muri ibyo bitekerezo; ndetse n'ingamba z'ibidukikije nko gusukura imyanya.
Ibihugu bindi na byo byafashe ingamba zitandukanye zigamije kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho ibizamini by'abantu benshi n'isonga ry'ubuvuzi, itanga imiburo ku myitwarire y'abanduye.
Singapour yahaye inkunga y'amafaranga abakomeretse biherereye kandi igahana amande menshi abatarayakoze.
Taiwan yongereye ibikorwa byo gukora udupfukamunwa kandi igabanya umubare w'ibicuruzwa by'ubuvuzi. Imikorere y'ubwigererane bw'u Bwongereza na Amerika igaragaza ko kugabanya (guhagarika icyorezo aho kugabanya) no kugabanya (gushyira mu gaciro ku cyorezo) bihangana n'ibibazo bikomeye.
Imishinga yo kugabanya ubwiyongere bw'ibyifuzo by'ubuzima ishobora kugabanya 2/3 n'urupfu ku kigero cya kabiri, ariko ikomeza gutuma abantu babarirwa mu bihumbi amagana bapfa kandi igatuma imibereho y'ubuzima irushaho guhangayika.
Kugabanya bishobora kuba byiza ariko bigomba gukomezwa igihe cyose virusi ikwirakwira mu bantu (cyangwa kugeza igihe urukingo ruzaba rubonetse, niba ari ubwa mbere), kuko guhita ku rundi ruhande bigaruka vuba iyo ingamba zitabaye ngombwa.
Kwinjira mu gihe kirekire mu guhashya icyorezo bibangamiye imibereho n'ubukungu.
Nta miti yihariye yo kurwanya virusi yemewe ya COVID-19, ariko hari ibikorwa byo guteza imbere, harimo no gupima imiti iriho.
Kunywa imiti yo kuvura icyorezo idakoreshwa n'abaganga, kunywa amazi n'ikiruhuko bishobora gufasha mu guhosha ibimenyetso.
Bitewe n'ubukana bw'iyo ndwara, bishobora kuba ngombwa ko umuntu ahumeka, akagira amazi mu misatsi, kandi akagira ubufasha bwo guhumeka.
Kunywa imiti ishobora gutuma ingaruka z'ibyo ugiye gukora zunyuka.
Ibikoresho byinshi byemewe mbere yo kuvura izindi ndwara za virusi bigomba gusuzumwa kugira ngo bikoreshwe mu kuvura COVID-19.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ryavuze kandi ko "imiti isanzwe n'iyo mu rugo" ishobora gutanga umuti wo kugabanya ibimenyetso byatewe na SARS-CoV-19.
Kwongera ubushobozi no guhangana n'ibigo by'ubuvuzi byo kwita ku barwayi ba COVID-19 byiswe n'umuryango w'abibumbye wita ku buzima (OMS) ingamba z'ingenzi zo guhangana n'icyorezo.
Ikigo cy'Ibihugu by'i Burayi gishinzwe kurwanya no gukumira indwara n'ibiro by'Umuryango w'Abibumbye by'Ubuzima (OMS) byashyizeho amabwiriza agenga ibitaro n'ubuvuzi bw'ibanze kugira ngo hakorwe ingufu ku rwego rwinshi, harimo gushyira imbaraga mu gupima COVID-19, guhagarika ingamba zo guhitamo aho bishoboka, gutandukanya COVID-19 n'abanduye no kubirinda, kongera ubushobozi bwo kwita ku bantu bafite uburwayi bw'umubiri binyuze mu gutoza abakozi no kongera umubare w'imashini zihumeka no mu muryango ziboneka.
Hari ibitekerezo byinshi ku birebana n'aho icyorezo cya mbere cyiswe "umurwayi wa Null " cyavuye.
Umuntu wa mbere wamenyekanye ko yaranduye coronavirus nshya ashobora kuba ari ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan, i Hobi, mu Bushinwa.
Mu gihe cy'ukwezi, umubare w'abanduye Coronavirus muri Hoby wiyongereye buhoro buhoro.
Ibi byiganjemo ibijyanye n'isoko ry'ibiribwa byo mu nyanja rya Wuhan, rigurisha n'inyamaswa nzima, kandi hari igitekerezo kivuga ko virusi yavuye muri imwe muri izo nyamaswa; cyangwa mu yandi magambo, ifite inkomoko y'inyamaswa. Itsinda ry'abafite uburwayi bw'ibihaha ku mpamvu itazwi ryabonetse ku wa 26 Ukuboza maze rivurwa na Dr. Zhang Jishian ku bitaro bya Hubei County, byabwiye Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara mu mujyi wa Jianghan Buhan ku wa 27 Ukuboza.
Ku itariki ya 30 Ukuboza, umugwi w'abaganga bo mu bitaro bya Wuhan Central warakanguriye bagenzi babo ko bafite "virusi ya Corona imeze nka SARS".
Polisi yahaye imiburo abaganga umunani barimo Li Wen Liang kugira ngo babwirwe ibinyoma, undi muganga witwa Ai Wen na we ahamagarwa n'abayobozi be kugira ngo aburire.
Komisiyo y'Ubuzima ya Komini ya Wuhan nyuma yaho yashyize ahagaragara itangazo rusange ku wa 31 Ukuboza maze ibimenyesha OMS.
Abategetsi b'ubuzima bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan barabonye amakuru ahagije y'ibimenyetso by'uburwayi bw'ibihaha bitamenyekana, bituma batangira iperereza mu ntangiriro za Mutarama. Mu bihe bya mbere by'icyorezo, umubare w'abanduye wikubye kabiri buri minsi irindwi n'igice.
Mu ntangiriro no hagati ya Mutarama 2020, virusi yageze mu bindi ntara byo mu Bushinwa, ifasha ingendo mu gihe cy'umwaka mushya w'u Bushinwa no kuba Wuhan ari ihuriro ry'ingendo n'aho imihanda y'umurenge mukuru ya gari ya moshi ihagarara.
Ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama, Ubushinwa bwavuze ko ku munsi umwe habayeho abantu bashya bagera ku 140, barimo abantu babiri i Beijing n'umwe i Shenzhen.
Amakuru yemewe yatangaje nyuma agaragaza ko abantu 6,174 bamaze kugaragaza ibimenyetso ku wa 20 Mutarama 2020. Ku wa 26 Werurwe, Amerika yarenze Ubushinwa n'u Butaliyani umubare munini w'abanduye ku isi. Ku wa 9 Mata 2020, amakuru yagaragaje ko hari abantu barenga miliyoni 1.61 ku isi, abantu barenga 97,000 bapfuye abandi barenga 364,000 barakira.
Ibihugu bigera kuri 200 n'uturere byanditseho nibura icyorezo kimwe.
Kubera icyorezo cy'ibicurane mu Burayi, ibihugu byinshi byo mu karere ka Shenzhen byafunze ubwisanzure bwo gutembera no gushyiraho imipaka.
Ibisubizo by'igihugu byibanze byatanze ingamba zo kwirinda, urugero nk'ubuvuzi (bwizwi nka "kugara mu rugo", "kujya ahantu", cyangwa "gufunga") no guhagarika ingendo. Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, abantu bagera kuri miliyoni 300, cyangwa hafi 90% by'abaturage, bari mu buryo runaka bwo gufunga muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, abantu barenga miriyoni 50 bo muri Filipine, abantu bagera kuri miriyoni 59 bo muri Afurika y'Epfo, naho abantu bagera kuri miriyari 1.3 bo mu Buhindi.
Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, abantu miliyari 1.7 ku isi yose bari mu buryo runaka bafunze, umubare waduze ugera kuri miriyari 2.6 nyuma y'iminsi ibiri - hafi kimwe cya gatatu cy'abatuye isi.
Icyorezo cya COVID-19 cya mbere cyemejwe ku itariki ya 1 Ukuboza 2019 i Wuhan; raporo imwe itari yemejwe ivuga ko icyorezo cya mbere cyabaye ku itariki ya 17 Ugushyingo.
Dr. Zhang Jiejian yabonye umubare w'abanduye indwara y'ubuhumekero bw'amaraso ku itariki ya 26 Ukuboza, kandi ku itariki ya 27 Ukuboza, yabitangarije ibitaro bye Ihuriro ry'Imitsi ry'i Jianghan Bohan.
Gusuzuma kwa mbere kwa Gene ku bipimo by'abarwayi ku wa 27 Ukuboza 2019 byerekanye ko hari virusi ya Corona isa na SARS.
Komisiyo y'Ubuzima ya Wuhan Municipal yafashe itangazo rusange ku itariki ya 31 Ukuboza.
Umuryango w'abibumbye wita ku buzima wabimenyeshejwe kuri uwo munsi.
Mu gihe hari aya makuru, abaganga bo mu mujyi wa Wuhan baburiwe n'igipolisi ko "bakwirakwiza ibihuha" ku byerekeye icyorezo.
Komisiyo y'igihugu y'ubuzima mu Bushinwa yabanje kuvuga ko nta "bihamya bifatika" byerekana ko umuntu ashobora guhita akura mu bandi.
Mu mpera za Mutarama, guverinoma y'Ubushinwa yatangije gahunda ikomeye yaje gusobanurwa na Shi Jinping, umunyamabanga mukuru w'ishyaka ry'abakomunisiti ryo mu Bushinwa, ko ari "intambara y'abaturage" yo guhashya ikwirakwira ry'iyi virusi.
Mu byo bise "Ibuye rikomeye cyane ry'ubuzima mu mateka y'abantu", ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama, hatangajwe ko hari umugogo w'ubuzima wo guhagarika ingendo ziva i Wuhan n'aho zijya, ugera ku mijyi 15 muri Hobi, bigira ingaruka ku bantu bagera kuri miliyoni 57.
Imodoka yihariye ntizikoreshwa mu mujyi.
Ibirori byo kwizihiza umwaka mushya w'u Bushinwa (25 Mutarama) byahagaritswe ahantu hatandukanye.
Abategetsi batangaje kandi ko bubaka ibitaro by'agateganyo, ibitaro bya Ho Chienshan, byuzuye mu minsi 10.
Nyuma yaho, hari undi bitaro byubatswe, ni ukuvuga Ibitaro bya Lichenshan, kugira ngo bifate abandi barwayi.
Uretse ibitaro bishya byashinzwe, Ubushinwa bwahinduye ibindi bigo 14 byo mu mujyi wa Wuhan, nko mu bigo by'amakoraniro n'ibibuga by'imikino, mu bitaro by'agateganyo. Ku wa 26 Mutarama, guverinoma yafashe izindi ngamba zo guhangana n'icyorezo cya COVID-19, harimo gutanga itangazo ry'ubuzima ku bagenzi no kwagura ikiruhuko cy'umunsi mukuru w'igihe cya mbere.
Kaminuza n'amashuri na byo byafunzwe hirya no hino mu gihugu.
Akarere ka Hong Kong na Macau kafashe ingamba nyinshi cyane cyane ku bijyanye n'amashuri na kaminuza.
Imikorere yo gukora ku birometero bya kure yafatiwe mu turere dutandukanye two mu Bushinwa.
Hariho amategeko agenga ingendo mu mujyi wa Hobi no hanze yawo.
Ibikoresho by'ubwikorezi byavuguruwe, inzu ndangamurage zo mu Bushinwa zose zafunzwe by'agateganyo.
Mu mijyi myinshi, abantu benshi bari bahagaritswe, kandi bivugwa ko abantu bagera kuri miriyoni 760 (abarenga kimwe cya kabiri cy'abaturage) bagizweho uburyo runaka bwo guhagarika kujya hanze. Nyuma y'aho icyorezo cyabaye icy'isi yose muri Werurwe, abategetsi b'u Bushinwa bafashe ingamba zikomeye zo kwirinda "kuzana" virusi mu bindi bihugu.
Urugero, Beijing yashinze abantu bose bagaruka mu mujyi baturutse mu bindi bihugu ibuye ry'ubuzima ry'iminsi 14. Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, hari umuntu umwe wageze mu gihugu cy'u Bushinwa mu minsi itanu ishize, ari mu nzira igana i Guangzhou avuye i Istanbul.
Ku itariki ya 24 Werurwe 2020, Perezida Li Keqiang wa Komite y'Igihugu y'Ubushinwa yatangaje ko icyorezo cy'indwara zandurira mu gihugu cya China cyagabanutse.
Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe 2020, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'u Bushinwa yatangaje ko kwinjira kw'abafite viza cyangwa ibyangombwa by'ubwami byahagaritswe guhera ku itariki ya 28 Werurwe, nta byimbitse birambuye ku gihe iyo politiki izarangira.
Abashaka kwinjira mu Bushinwa bazajya basabwa gusaba viza muri ambasade cyangwa muri konsulatari z'u Bushinwa.
Guverinoma y'u Bushinwa yasabye ibigo n'inganda kongera gukora ku wa 30 Werurwe, kandi itanga inkunga y'amafaranga ku bigo. Inama y'Igihugu yatangaje umunsi wo kurira utangira umunota umwe wo guceceka ku wa 4 Mata saa kumi n'ebyiri, ku gihe cya Qingming Festival, nubwo guverinoma y'u Bushinwa yasabye imiryango kugaragaza icyubahiro cyabo kuri interineti mu kubahiriza gutandukanywa kw'umubiri kugira ngo birinde icyorezo cya COVID-19 cyongera.
COVID-19 yageze muri Koreya y'Epfo kuva mu Bushinwa ku itariki ya 20 Mutarama 2020.
Ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima cyatangaje ko ku itariki ya 20 Gashyantare habayeho kwiyongera kw'abanduye, kandi ibyo byatewe inkunga cyane n'uko mu mujyi wa Daegu hagiye guteraniraho umuryango mushya w'idini uzwi ku izina rya Shincheongji Church of Jesus.
Abafana ba Shincheongji baza gusura Daegu bavuye i Wuhan, bakekwaho kuba ari bo bateje iki cyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 22 Gashyantare, abantu 1,261 cyangwa 13% by'abayoboke ba Kiliziya 9,336 bari bafite ibimenyetso. Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko ku itariki ya 23 Gashyantare 2020 ari ho yari ifite umubare munini w'abantu bari biteguye.
Ku itariki ya 28 Gashyantare, muri Koreya hemejwe ko hari abantu barenga 2,000 banduye, aho ku itariki ya 29 Gashyantare habonetse abantu 3.150.
Ibigo byose bya gisirikare bya Koreya y'Epfo byashyizwe mu kato nyuma y'uko ibizamini byemeza ko abasirikare batatu banduye iyi virusi.
Ibihe by'indege nabyo byarafashwe, hanyuma birahinduka. Koreya y'Epfo yashyizeho gahunda yari izwi nk'iya mbere ku isi yo gusuzuma abantu kugira ngo bashobore kubona virusi, bakarinda abanduye, bakagenzura abababonye kandi bakabashyira mu kato.
Uburyo bwo gusuzuma bwari bukubiyemo gutanga amakuru y'ibimenyetso ku buntu ku bashya baje mu mahanga binyuze kuri porogaramu ya telefoni igendanwa, gupima virusi ku bantu bari mu modoka zabo ku munsi ukurikiyeho, no kongera ubushobozi bwo gupima abantu bagera ku 20,000 ku munsi.
Porogaramu ya Koreya y'Epfo yagaragaje ko yatsinze icyorezo nubwo nta mabuye y'isuku yashyizwe mu migi yose. Umuryango wa Koreya y'Epfo watangiye kwicamo ibice ku buryo Perezida Moon Jae-in yabyitabiriye.
Abanyakoreya benshi basinye ku bisabwa byo gusaba ko Moon yajya mu gisirikare, bavuga ko leta ititaye ku ndwara cyangwa se bashimira uko yabyitabiriye.
Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, Koreya y'Epfo yatangaje ko ifite abanduye ku munsi umwe ku munsi muto mu byumweru bine.
Ku itariki ya 29 Werurwe, byatangajwe ko guhera ku itariki ya 1 Mata, abimukira bashya bose bavuye hanze bazaba bari mu kato mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Nkuko raporo z'itangazamakuru zo ku itariki ya 1 Mata zabitangaje, Koreya y'Epfo yahawe ibisabwa n'ibihugu 121 bitandukanye byo gufasha gupima virusi.
Irani yatangaje ko ku itariki ya 19 Gashyantare, abantu babiri bapfuye nyuma y'umunsi umwe, nk'uko Minisiteri y'Ubuzima n'Uburezi bw'Ubuvuzi yabitangaje.
Mu ngamba za mbere leta yatangaje harimo guhagarika ibitaramo n'ibindi bikorwa by'umuco n'imikino, gusenga ku wa gatanu, gufunga kaminuza, ibigo by'amashuri yisumbuye n'amashuri.
Irani yashyize hanze miliyari eshanu z'amafaranga y'u Rwanda mu kurwanya iyi virusi.
Perezida Hassan Rouhani yatangaje ku wa 26 Gashyantare 2020 ko nta gahunda yo gutema amabuye mu bice byatewe n'icyorezo, abantu bonyine nibo bazajya bavangwa.
Inshingano zo kugabanya ingendo hagati y'imijyi zatangajwe muri Werurwe, nubwo imihanda myinshi ikomeje gutembera mbere y'umwaka mushya w'umuco wa Peresi.
Imigi y'aba Shi'ite i Qom yagumye yuguruye abapadiri kugeza ku wa 16 Werurwe 2020. Mu kwezi kwa Gashyantare, Irani yabaye ihuriro ry'icyorezo cya Virusi nyuma y'Ubushinwa.
Mu gihe hari ibirego by'uko Iran yashyize ahagaragara icyorezo cyayo, ibihugu birenga icumi byakurikiranye abakijijwe bavuye muri Irani guhera ku wa 28 Gashyantare, ibyo bikaba byerekana ko icyorezo gishobora kurenga 388 byatangajwe na guverinoma ya Irani kugeza icyo gihe.
Inteko Ishinga Amategeko ya Irani yafunzwe, aho ku itariki ya 3 Werurwe, abantu 23 mu bagize Inteko Ishinga Amategeko 290 bagaragaye ko banduye iyi virusi.
Ku itariki ya 12 Werurwe, Human Rights Watch yasabye abayobozi ba gereza za Irani kurekura abantu barwanira uburenganzira bafunzwe bazira imyigaragambyo y'amahoro, ndetse no kurekura imfungwa zifite ibyangombwa.
Yavuze ko hari akaga gakomeye ko gukwirakwira kwa virusi mu bibanza byafunze nko mu bigo by'imbohe, kandi aho nta buvuzi buhagije buhari.
Ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, guverinoma ya Irani yatangaje ko abantu 100 bapfuye mu munsi umwe, ari umubare munini w'abapfuye umaze kwandura muri icyo gihugu kuva icyo cyorezo cyatangira.
Abantu 12 ku isi, baba abanyapolitiki ba Irani, abayobozi ba Leta n'abahozeho, bapfuye bazize iyo ndwara kugeza ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe.
Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, Irani yari imaze kubona abantu bashya 50 banduye icyorezo cya Corona mu isaha imwe, n'umuntu umwe upfa buri minota icumi.
Umukozi wa OMS avuga ko umubare w'abanduye muri Irani ushobora kuba inshuro eshanu z'abatangajwe.
Bitekerezwa kandi ko ibihano Amerika yafatiye Irani bishobora kugira ingaruka ku bushobozi bw'igihugu bwo guhangana n'icyorezo cya virusi.
Komisiyo nkuru y'umuryango w'abibumbye y'uburenganzira bwa muntu yasabye ko ibihano by'ubukungu by'ibihugu byugarijwe cyane n'iki cyorezo, harimo na Irani, byoroha.
Icyorezo cy'indwara ya SARS-CoV-2 cyemejwe mu Butaliyani ku wa 31 Mutarama, ubwo abashakashatsi b'Abashinwa bari i Roma bageragezaga ko ari ingirakamaro.
Ibibazo byatangiye kwiyongera cyane, bituma leta y'u Butaliyani ihagarika ingendo zose z'indege ziva mu Bushinwa zijya muri icyo gihugu, ndetse itangaza ko habaye imimerere y'ubutabire.
Nyuma habonetse itsinda ry'abantu badafite aho bahuriye na COVID-19, hatangirana n'abamaze kwandura 16 i Lombardy ku wa 21 Gashyantare. Ku wa 22 Gashyantare, Inama y'Abaminisitiri yatangaje itegeko rishya ryo gukumira icyorezo, harimo no gukumira abantu barenga 50,000 bo mu migi 11 itandukanye yo mu majyaruguru y'u Butaliyani.
Minisitiri w'Intebe Giuseppe Conte yagize ati "Ntibizemerwa kwinjira cyangwa gusohoka mu duce twugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Hariho itegeko ryo guhagarika ibikorwa n'imikino muri utwo duce". Ku wa 4 Werurwe, leta y'u Butaliyani yategetse ko amashuri yose na kaminuza bifungwa burundu mu gihugu hose, aho abapfuye mu Butaliyani bageze ku 100.
Imikino yose ikomeye ya siporo, harimo imikino ya shampiyona y'umupira w'amaguru, yari iteganyijwe kubera inyuma y'inzugi zifunze kugeza muri Mata, ariko ku itariki ya 9 Werurwe, imikino yose ya siporo yahagaritswe burundu mu gihe cy'ukwezi kumwe nibura.
Ku itariki ya 11 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Conti yategetse ko ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi hafi ya byose bihagarara, uretse ibigo by'ubucuruzi n'ubuvuzi. Ku itariki ya 6 Werurwe, Ishuri ry'Igihugu ry'Ubutabire, Ubutabazi, Ubuzima n'Ibitunga (SIAARTI) ryasohoye inama z'amategeko y'ubuvuzi ku bijyanye n'amabwiriza yo gutandukanya ashobora gukoreshwa.
Ku wa 19 Werurwe, Ubutaliyani bwatsinze Ubushinwa nk'igihugu cyabonye umubare munini w'abapfuye ba Coronavirus ku isi nyuma yo gutanga amakuru y'abantu 3,405 bapfuye kubera iki cyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, u Burusiya bwohereje indege icyenda za gisirikare zitwaye ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi mu Butaliyani.
Ku itariki ya 5 Mata, hari abantu 128,948 bamaze kwandura, abantu 15,887 bapfuye, mu Butaliyani habayeho abantu 21,815, abenshi muri bo bakaba bari mu karere ka Lombardy.
Raporo ya CNN yagaragaje ko kubamo umubare munini w'abageze mu za bukuru n'ubushobozi buke bwo gupima abantu bose banduye virusi kugeza ubu mu Butaliyani bishobora kuba byaratumye umubare w'abapfa wiyongera.
Ubwongereza bwabanje kugaragara ko ari bwo bwifashe nabi cyane mu bihugu byugarijwe n'iyo virusi, kandi kugeza ku wa 18 Werurwe 2020, guverinoma y'u Bwongereza ntiyahatiraga abaturage bayo uburyo ubwo ari bwo bwose bwo kwirinda abantu cyangwa kwirinda ubuzima.
Ibi byatumye Leta isuzumwa kubera ko itagize icyo ikora vuba kandi ikavuga cyane ku bibazo byugarije abaturage. Ku wa 16 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe Boris Johnson yashyize ahagaragara itangazo ryamugira inama yo kwirinda ingendo zidakenewe cyangwa guhungabanya imibanire y'abantu, agasaba abantu gukora bava mu rugo uko bishoboka kose kandi bakirinda ahantu hatandukanye, nko mu tubyiniro, mu mirima n'ibibuga by'imikino.
Ku itariki ya 20 Werurwe, guverinoma yatangaje ko izafunga ibikorwa byose by'imyidagaduro nk'ababyiniro n'amazu y'imikino vuba bishoboka, kandi isezeranya ko izatanga amafaranga agera kuri 80% y'imishahara y'abakozi igera ku £2,500 ku kwezi kugira ngo igabanure ubushomeri mu gihe cy'ikibazo. Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, Minisitiri w'Intebe yatangaje ingamba zikomeye cyane z'ubutabanganyi, aho imikorere y'abantu benshi yari ihagaritswe, kandi ko kugenda no gukora ibikorwa hanze y'inzu byari bibujijwe uretse mu gihe cy'ibanze.
Mu buryo butandukanye n'uko byari bimeze mbere, izi mpapuro z'ubucamanza zashyizweho n'abapolisi mu gutanga amande no gusenya imyanya y'abantu.
Amategeko yahagaritse ibikorwa byinshi by'ubucuruzi, uretse ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi "bikwiriye", harimo ibigo by'ubucuruzi, amafarmasi, amabanki, ibigo by'ibikoresho, ibigo by'ibitoro bya lisansi n'ibigo by'ubworozi.
Tariki ya 20 Mutarama, icyorezo cya COVID-19 cya mbere cyemejwe mu ntara ya Washington mu majyaruguru ashyira uburengerazuba bwa Pasifika ku mugabo wasubiye i Wuhan ku itariki ya 15 Mutarama.
Itsinda ry'abakozi ba White House ryo kurwanya Coronavirus ryashyizweho tariki ya 29 Mutarama.
Ku itariki ya 31 Mutarama, ubutegetsi bwa Trump bwatangaje ko hari ibintu byihutirwa mu buzima bwa rusange, buhagarika abagenzi bava mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 28 Mutarama 2020, Ikigo gishinzwe kurwanya indwara, ikigo cy'igihugu gishinzwe ubuzima rusange cya Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, cyatangaje ko cyatangije itsinda ry'imishinga.
Nubwo Amerika yakoze ibyo, yatinze gutangira gukora igeragezwa, bituma icyo gihe ubwirinzi bw'icyo cyorezo bugabanuka.
Iki kigeragezo cyayogoje urutonde rw'igeragezwa ridafite aho rugarukira ryagaragaye muri Gashyantare, kubura kwemererwa na Leta ku matsinda y'igeragezwa atari aya leta (ni ukuvuga abanyeshuri, ibigo by'ubucuruzi n'ibitaro) kugeza mu mpera za Gashyantare, n'ibisabwa abantu bari bafite byo kwitabira iki kigeragezo kugeza mu ntangiriro za Werurwe (nyuma y'aho itegeko ry'umuganga ryari rikenewe).
Ku itariki ya 27 Gashyantare, ikinyamakuru Washington Post cyavuze ko nta miti 4,000 y'ubuvuzi yari imaze gukorwa muri Amerika.
Ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, ikinyamakuru The Atlantic cyavuze ko hari hasigaye ibizamini 14.000.
Ku itariki ya 22 Werurwe, The Associated Press yatangaje ko "abantu benshi bafite ibimenyetso kandi bafite itegeko ry'umuganga bategereje amasaha cyangwa iminsi yo gupima". Nyuma yo gutangazwa k'urupfu rwa mbere muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika muri leta ya Washington ku itariki ya 29 Gashyantare, Guverineri Jay Insley yatangaje imimerere y'ubutagondwa, igikorwa cyahise gikurikirwa n'indi mirenge.
Amashuri yo mu mujyi wa Seattle yahagaritse amasomo ku ya 3 Werurwe, maze mu giharage cy'ukwezi kwa Werurwe, amashuri yo hirya no hino mu gihugu arafungwa. Ku ya 6 Werurwe 2020, Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika zabwiwe ku byerekeranye n'ingaruka za Coronavirus nshya ku gihugu n'abahanga mu by'indwara z'ibyorezo bo muri Imperial College University of London.
Kuri uwo munsi Perezida Trump yashyize umukono ku itegeko ry'ibikoresho by'ubwishingizi byo kwitegura no guhangana na Coronavirus, ryatanze inkunga yihutirwa y'amadolari miliyari 8.3 ku bigo bya leta kugira ngo bigire icyo bigeraho mu guhangana n'icyorezo.
Ibigo by'ubucuruzi byashyizeho amategeko abuza abakozi gukora, byasenyura amakoraniro, kandi byashishikarije abakozi gukora imirimo yo mu rugo.
Imikino n'ibihe by'imikino byahagaritswe. Ku wa 11 Werurwe, Trump yatangaje ko hari iminsi 30 azamara agamije guhagarika ingendo mu Burayi bwose, uretse mu Bwongereza, guhera ku wa 13 Werurwe.
Ku munsi wakurikiyeho, ibyo bihano byongerewe no mu Bwongereza no muri Irilande.
Ku itariki ya 13 Werurwe, yatangaje imimerere y'ubutagondwa, yemerera gukoresha amafaranga ya Leta kugira ngo ahangane n'ikibazo.
Guhera ku itariki ya 15 Werurwe, amashyirahamwe menshi yafunze cyangwa agabanya amasaha yo gukora hirya no hino muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe z'Amerika mu kugerageza kugabanya ikwirakwira rya virusi.
Ku itariki ya 17 Werurwe, icyorezo cyari cyemejwe mu majyaruguru ya Amerika no mu ntara ya Columbia. Ku itariki ya 23 Werurwe, abantu 10.700 banduye Coronavirus mu mujyi wa New York City, ni ukuvuga umubare munini cyane ugereranyije n'uw'abanduye muri Koreya y'Epfo.
Ku wa 25 Werurwe, Guverineri yavuze ko kubana n'abantu mu buryo bw'imibereho bigaragara ko byagenze neza, kuko ibipimo byerekana ko ubwandu bwagabanutse kuva ku minsi 2.0 kugeza ku minsi 4.7.
Ku itariki ya 28 Werurwe, hari abantu 32.308 banduye muri New York City, abantu 672 bapfuye bazize virusi. Ku itariki ya 26 Werurwe, hari abantu benshi cyane banduye virusi ya Corona muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika kurusha abandi mu isi, harimo u Bushinwa n'u Butaliyani. Ku itariki ya 8 Mata, abantu 400,335 banduye muri Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika, abantu 12,841 bapfuye.
Nkuko byatangajwe n'itangazamakuru ku wa 30 Werurwe, Perezida wa Amerika Trump yafashe icyemezo cyo kongera amabwiriza yo kwirinda abantu kugeza ku wa 30 Mata.
Kuri uwo munsi, ubwato bw'ibitaro bufite ibitanda bigera ku 1000 bwa USS Comfort bwarohamye i New York.
Ku itariki ya 3 Mata, Amerika yongeyeho abantu 884 bahitanywe na coronavirus mu masaha 24.
Mu ntara ya New York, umubare w'abanduye warenze 100,000 abantu ku itariki ya 3 Mata. Ibiro by'ibanze by'Igihugu byashyizwehoho impaka ku bijyanye no kugabanya iterabwoba no kugenzura ikwirakwira ry'amakuru binyuze mu kuyobora abayobozi b'ubuzima n'abahanga mu by'ubuzima guhuza amakuru rusange n'ibitangazamakuru bijyanye na virusi hamwe n'ibiro bya Visi Perezida Mike Pence.
Ubutegetsi bwa Trump ntibwashimishijwe cyane n'ikibazo cy'imvururu kuko bwatumye amashyaka menshi aterana.
Bamwe mu bayobozi ba Amerika n'abanyamakuru banenze uburyo Amerika ikoresha mu kwinjiza ibintu by'ibanze, harimo n'ibikoresho by'ibanze by'ubuvuzi, mu Bushinwa.
Isesengura ry'ingendo z'indege ryakoreshejwe mu gukora ikarita y'ingendo z'indege no kuzihanura, ryasohotse mu kinyamakuru cy'ubuvuzi bw'ingendo mu kwezi kwa Mutarama 2020.
Dukurikije amakuru ya International Air Transport Union 2018, Bangkok, Hong Kong, Tokyo na Taipei bifite abagenzi benshi cyane baturutse i Wuhan.
Dubai, Sydney na Melbourne na byo byatangajwe ko ari ahantu hazwi cyane ku bavuye i Wuhan.
Bali yamenyeshejwe ko ari yo ifite ubushobozi buke cyane mu bihugu 20 by'ingenzi mu bijyanye no kuba yiteguye, mu gihe imijyi yo muri Australia ari yo ifite ubushobozi bwinshi. Australia yashyize hanze gahunda yayo yo guhangana na Coronavirus nshya (COVID-19) ku itariki ya 7 Gashyantare.
Yavuze ko nta byinshi byamenyekanye kuri COVID-19, kandi ko Australia izashyira imbaraga mu gucunga imipaka no guhuza amakuru mu guhangana n'icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 21 Werurwe, Australia yatangaje ko hari ibintu by'ibanze by'umutekano w'ibinyabuzima.
Kubera ko ingendo z'abantu benshi zagize ingaruka ku buzima bwiza bw'i Wuhan n'i Hobi, ibihugu byinshi byateganyaga ko abaturage babyo n'abakozi babyo bavuye muri ako karere, mbere na mbere binyuze mu ndege zifatirwa mu gihugu cyabo, mu gihe abategetsi b'u Bushinwa batanga impushya.
Canada, Amerika, Ubuyapani, Ubuhinde, Sri Lanka, Ositaraliya, Ubufaransa, Arjantine, Ubudage na Tayilande ni bimwe mu bihugu bya mbere byateguye guhunga abaturage babyo.
Pakistan yatangaje ko itazongera gutumiza abaturage bayo mu Bushinwa.
Ku itariki ya 7 Gashyantare, Brezili yavanye muri yombi Abanya Brezili 34 cyangwa abantu bafunzwe, hamwe n'Abanyapolonye bane, umuntu umwe w'Umushinwa n'Umuhindi.
Abaturage b'Abanyapolonye, Abashinwa n'Abahinde bavuye mu ndege muri Polonye, aho indege ya Brazil yahagaze mbere y'uko itangira urugendo rwayo rwo kujya muri Brezili.
Abaturage ba Brazil bagiye i Wuhan, bashyizwe mu kato ku kigo cya gisirikare kiri hafi ya Brazil.
Kuri uwo munsi, Abakanada 215 (176 bo mu ndege ya mbere, 39 bo mu ndege ya kabiri yahawe leta ya Amerika) bavuye i Wuhan bajya ku kigo cy'ingabo za Canada cya Trenton mu gihe cy'ibyumweru bibiri.
Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare, indi ndege yari itwaye Abanyakanada 185 yavuye i Wuhan, yahanuye ku kigo cy'ingabo za Canada cya Trenton.
Ku itariki ya 3 n'iya 4 Gashyantare, abategetsi ba Australia bajyanye abaturage 277 mu kigo cy'ibohero cya Christmas Island, cyongeye gukoreshwa nk'ikigo cy'amabuye y'isuku, aho bamaraga iminsi 14.
Indege yo kuvana muri Nouvelle-Zélande yageze i Auckland ku ya 5 Gashyantare, maze abagenzi bayo (harimo abantu baturutse muri Australia no mu nyanja ya Pasifika) baregurwa ku kigo cya gisirikare cya Wanjambarawa mu majyaruguru ya Auckland.
Ku itariki ya 15 Gashyantare, Leta Zunze Ubumwe za Amerika zatangaje ko zizata abanyamerika bari ku bwato bwa Diamond Princess.
Ku itariki ya 21 Gashyantare, indege y'indege y'Abanyamerika 129 yavuye mu bwato bwa Diamond Princess yageze i Trenton muri Ontario.
Mu ntangiriro z'ukwezi kwa gatatu, Leta y'u Buhinde yatangiye guhunga abaturage bayo bava muri Irani. Ku itariki ya 14 Werurwe, indege ya South African Airlines yari yarashyizwe mu kazi na Leta ya Afurika y'Epfo yashubije abaturage 112 bo muri Afurika y'Epfo.
Mbere yo kugenda, abaganga babagerageza, maze abantu bane bo muri Afurika y'Epfo bagaragaye ibimenyetso bya virusi ya Corona bagasigaye kugira ngo bareke guhangana n'iki kibazo.
Abanyarwanda bo mu majyepfo bavuye mu gihugu cyabo bavuye mu gihugu cyabo gusa.
Ibisubizo by'ibipimo byemeje ko Abanyafurika y'Epfo, harimo abakozi b'indege, abapayiniya, abakozi ba hoteli, abapolisi n'abasirikare bari mu gikorwa cy'ubutabazi bose bagumye, nk'uburyo bwo kwirinda, bari mu isanzure n'isuku mu kigo cy'ubworozi cya Ranch mu gihe cy'iminsi 14, nta cyo bakomeretse.
Ku itariki ya 20 Werurwe, Amerika yatangiye gukura ingabo zayo muri Iraq mu buryo bwuzuye kubera icyorezo.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, Minisiteri y'Ububanyi n'Amahanga y'u Bushinwa yatangaje ko ibihugu 21 (harimo u Bushinwa, Pakistan, Trinidad, Tobago, Misiri na Irani) byohereje ubufasha mu Bushinwa.
Abanyeshuri b'Abashinwa bo muri za kaminuza zo muri Amerika bashyize hamwe kohereza imfashanyo mu duce twanduye virusi mu Bushinwa, kandi nk'uko bivugwa, itsinda rihuriye mu karere ka Chicago ryashoboye kohereza udupfukamunwa 50,000 tw'ubwoko bwa N95 ku bitaro byo mu ntara ya Hubei ku wa 30 Mutarama. Umuryango w'ubutabazi bw'abantu Direct Relief, uhuza na FedEx, woherereje udupfukamunwa 200,000 hamwe n'ibindi bikoresho by'ubwirinzi bwite, harimo ingofero n'imyenda by'abakozi bo mu bitaro, binyuze ku kiraro cy'ubutabazi bw'ikirere, ku bitaro bya Wuhan Union ku wa 30 Mutarama.
Ku itariki ya 5 Gashyantare, Bill na Melinda Gates batangaje ko batanze miliyoni 100 z'amadolari ku muryango w'isi yose wita ku buzima kugira ngo bishyireho amafaranga mu bushakashatsi bw'inkingo no mu bikorwa byo kuvura, ndetse no kurinda "abaturage bari mu kaga muri Afurika no muri Aziya y'Epfo".
Interraceon yatangaje ko leta y'Ubushinwa yatanze udupfukamunwa 200,000 kuri Philippines kuwa 6 Gashyantare, nyuma y'uko Senateri Richard Gordon yohereje udupfukamunwa miliyoni 3.16 i Wuhan.
Ku itariki ya 19 Gashyantare, Ibara ry'Umuryango w'Abarabu wa Singapore watangaje ko ugiye kohereza inkunga ya miliyoni 2.26 z'amadolari mu Bushinwa.
U Buyapani bwahaye u Wuhan udupfukamunwa tw'uruhu miliyoni, u Turukiya butuma ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, u Burusiya butuma toni zisaga 13 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi i Wuhan, Malaysia itangaza ko yatanze amakanzu y'ubuvuzi miliyoni 18 ku Bushinwa, u Budage butanga ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi bitandukanye birimo imyenda ikingira 10,000, Amerika itanga u Bushinwa toni 17.8 z'ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi, kandi isezeranya gutanga inkunga y'amafaranga y'andi miriyoni 100 y'amadolari ku bihugu byugarijwe n'icyorezo.
Muri Werurwe, Ubushinwa, Cuba n'Uburusiya byohereje ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi n'abahanga bo gufasha u Butaliyani guhangana n'icyorezo cya Coronavirus.
Umushoramari Jack Ma yohereje mu mujyi wa Addis Ababa muri Ethiopia miliyoni 1.1 z'amakipe yo gupima, miliyoni 6 z'amasiki n'imyenda 60 000 y'ubwirinzi aho ishyirahamwe ry'ubumwe bwa Afurika ryabitanze.
Nyuma yo kohereza muri Panama, yohereje amatsinda 5000 y'imibonano mpuzabitsina, udupfukamunwa 100,000 n'imashini 5 zo guhumeka.
Ma kandi yahaye Canada ibikoresho by'ubuvuzi. U Buholandi, Esipanye, Turukiya, Jeworujiya na Repubulika ya Czech byatanze impungenge ku masiki n'ibipimo byakozwe mu Bushinwa.
Urugero, Espagne yafashe amasomo 58 000 y'icyorezo cya Corona yakorewe mu Bushinwa, afite igipimo cya 30% gusa, mu gihe kimwe, Ubuholandi bwasubije amasikuru 600.000 y'amaso yakorewe mu Bushinwa yari afite ikibazo.
Ububiligi bwasubije mu Bubiligi udupfukamunwa 100,000 tutakoreshwa twitwa ko twavuye mu Bushinwa, ariko mu by'ukuri twavuye muri Kolombiya.
Ku rundi ruhande, ibice byo muri Amerika y'Epfo na Afurika byishimiye ko inkunga y'Ubushinwa yahawe neza. Ku itariki ya 2 Mata, Banki y'Isi yatangije ibikorwa by'ubutabazi mu bihe by'ubukene ku bihugu biri mu nzira y'amajyambere.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima rishimye imihati y'ubutegetsi bw'u Bushinwa mu gucunga iki cyorezo no kucyirinda.
Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima ryavuze itandukaniro riri hagati y'icyorezo cya SARS cyo mu 2002 na 2004, aho abategetsi b'Ubushinwa bashinjwa ko cyatumye abantu batagira icyo bakora mu kwirinda no kubigumana, n'ikibazo kiriho ubu, aho leta nkuru y'u Bushinwa yatanze "iminsi mikuru ihoraho yo kwirinda ubwoba mbere y'iminsi mikuru y'umwaka mushya w'ukwezi".
Ku itariki ya 23 Mutarama, mu gusubiza ku mwanzuro w'ubutegetsi bw'igihugu wo gushyiraho itegeko ribuza uburyo bwo gutwara abantu mu mujyi wa Wuhan, umuvugizi wa WHO Gooden Gallaya yavuze ko nubwo "nta gushidikanya ko ari inama ya WHO", "ari ikimenyetso gikomeye cyane cy'uko icyorezo kigomba guhagarikwa aho kigaragarira cyane", avuga ko "kitari bwigere kibaho mu mateka y'ubuzima rusange". Ku itariki ya 30 Mutarama, nyuma yo kwemeza ko umuntu yagiye hanze y'u Bushinwa, n'umubare w'abanduye mu bindi bihugu wiyongereye, WHO yatangaje ko icyorezo ari ihungabana ry'ubuzima rusange ry'intera ku rwego mpuzamahanga (PHEAC), ari nacyo cya gatandatu cyatumye ibihugu by'isi byakira abantu mu buryo bw'igitangaza kuva mu mwaka wa 2009.
Umuyobozi mukuru wa OMS yavuze ko icyorezo cyiswe nk'ihungabana ry'ubuzima rusange ry'intera ku rwego mpuzamahanga kubera "akaga ko gukwirakwira ku isi hose, cyane cyane mu bihugu bifite amikoro make n'ayigereranyije bidafite gahunda zikomeye z'ubuzima.
Mu gusubiza ku itegekonshinga ry'ingamba zo guhagarika ingendo, Tedros yavuze ko "nta mpamvu yo gufata ingamba zitemewe zitanyuranyije n'ingendo n'ubucuruzi mpuzamahanga" kandi ko "Ishami ry'Umuryango w'Abibumbye ryita ku Buzima (OMS) ritagamije kugabanya ubucuruzi n'ingendo".
Ku wa 5 Gashyantare, OMS yasabye umuryango mpuzamahanga gutanga miliyoni 675 z'amadolari mu mikoreshereze y'ibihugu bifite amikoro make, igaragaza ko byihutirwa gushyigikira ibihugu "bitagira uburyo bwo gutahura abantu banduye virusi, niyo byaba byaragaragaye".
Tedros kandi yatanze amagambo avuga ko "imbaraga zacu zigereranywa n'imbaraga z'umuntu ufite intege nke kurusha abandi muri twe" kandi asaba umuryango mpuzamahanga "guhora ubu cyangwa kwishyura amafaranga menshi nyuma". Ku itariki ya 11 Gashyantare, OMS yatangije icyorezo, mu kiganiro n'abanyamakuru, yise COVID-19.
Kuri uwo munsi, Tedros yavuze ko Umunyamabanga Mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye, Antonio Guterres, yemeye gutanga "ubushobozi bw'isi yose y'Umuryango w'Abibumbye mu gusubiza".
Ibi byatumye hashyirwaho itsinda ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku bibazo by'amahangayiko, rifasha umuryango w'abibumbye guhuza igisubizo cyawo cyose, kandi OMS izaremera "gushyira imbaraga mu guhangana n'ikibazo cy'ubuzima mu gihe uburambe bw'izindi nzego bushobora gukoreshwa mu kumenya ingaruka rusange, ubukungu n'iterambere by'icyorezo".
Ku wa 14 Gashyantare, itsinda ry'itsinda ry'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) riyobowe n'umuryango w'abibumbye ryita ku buzima (OMS) ryashyizeho itsinda ry'abakozi ba ONU n'abakozi b'umuryango w'abibumbye b'ubuzima (WHO) mu Bushinwa kugira ngo batange impuguke mpuzamahanga n'abahanga bo ku isi (WHO) mu Bushinwa, bafashe mu bikorwa byo gucunga abaturage, no gusuzuma "ingaruka z'ibikorwa by'ubwibone ku rwego rw'intara n'imijyi, harimo n'imijyi n'imidugudu". Ku wa 25 Gashyantare, umuryango w'abibumbye wita ku buzima (WHO) watangaje ko "isi igomba gukora byinshi kugira ngo yitegure icyorezo cy'icyorezo cya coronavirus", ariko ko "iki cyorezo" cyagombaga kuba kiri mu cyiciro cya mbere cy'icyorezo.
Mu rwego rwo gusubiza ku cyorezo cyabaye muri Irani, OMS yohereje itsinda ry'umurimo ufatanyije muri icyo gihugu kugira ngo rigenzure uko ibintu byifashe. Ku wa 28 Gashyantare, abayobozi ba OMS bavuze ko igenzura ry'igitero cya Coronavirus ku rwego rw'isi rizamuka kuva ku "kirenga" rigera ku "kirenga cyane", ari nacyo kigero cyo hejuru cyo kuburira no gupima akaga.
Mike Ryan, umuyobozi mukuru w'Umuryango w'Abibumbye wita ku buzima mu bihe by'impanuka, mu itangazo rye, yatanze umuburo agira ati "iki ni ikigeragezo cy'ukuri kuri buri butegetsi bwose ku isi: tugomba kuba twiteguye.
Iyi virusi ishobora kuba iri mu nzira, kandi mugomba kuyitegura, kandi asaba ko hafatwa ingamba zo kugira icyo bikorwa neza bishobora gufasha isi kwirinda "ibibi kurushaho".
