Ibi bikorwa by'ubucuruzi bigamije kureba uko ibiciro by'ibyago by'akazi n'akazi byagiye byiyongera, harimo aho umuntu ashobora guhurira n'ibyago, ibyago by'inzu n'aho abantu bahurira n'abandi, ndetse n'ibyago by'abakozi ku giti cyabo, urugero nk'iza bukuru cyangwa indwara z'igihe kirekire.
Nanone kandi, hashyizweho amategeko agenga uko ibyo bintu bishobora kubaho, n'ingamba z'ubutabazi z'imimerere ishobora guterwa n'icyorezo.
Imigambi yo guhora witeguye no guhangana n'indwara zandura ishobora gukurikizwa n'inama z'igihugu ndetse n'iz'amahanga.
Intego zo gusubiza icyorezo zirimo kugabanya kwandura hagati y'abakozi, kurinda abantu bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara, gukomeza ibikorwa by'ubucuruzi no kugabanya ingaruka mbi ku zindi nzego mu mitororokano yazo.
Uburemere bw'indwara mu muryango w'ubucuruzi bugira ingaruka ku byo umuntu yitabira.
Urutonde rw'ibanze rw'imihati yo kugenzura ibyago ni uburyo bukoreshwa cyane mu bijyanye n'umutekano n'ubuzima bw'akazi mu gushyiraho ingamba zo kugenzura ibyago ku bw'uko bikora.
Kubera ko ibyago bya COVID-19 bidashobora gukurwaho, inzego z'ubugenzuzi ni zo zifite ingufu kurusha izindi, zikurikirwa n'iz'ubuyobozi, hanyuma zikurikirwa n'ibikoresho byo kwirinda.
Ubugenzuzi bw'ubuhinzi bugira uruhare mu gutuma abakozi birinda ibyago byo gukora nta gushingira ku myitwarire y'abakozi, kandi bishobora kuba umuti mwiza cyane ku bijyanye n'igiciro cyo gukora.
Ubuyobozi bw'ubuyobozi ni impinduka mu politiki y'akazi cyangwa ingamba zisaba ko umukozi cyangwa umukoresha akora.
Ibikoresho byo kurinda umuntu ku giti cye (PBE) ni byiza cyane kurusha ibipimo by'ubugenzuzi n'ubuyobozi, ariko bishobora gufasha mu kwirinda ahantu runaka h'ibishushanyo.
Ibikoresho byose by'ubwirinzi by'umuntu ku giti cye bigomba gutorwa hashingiwe ku kaga umukozi ashyigikiwe, kuba bikwiye uko bikenewe (nk'ibyuma bihumeka), kwambara buri gihe kandi mu buryo bukwiriye, gusuzuma, kwitaho no gusimbuza buri gihe, uko bikenewe, gukuraho, gusukura no kubika, cyangwa gutakaza neza kugira ngo wirinde kwandura.
Dukurikije ubuyobozi bw'igihugu bw'ubuvuzi n'umutekano mu kazi muri Amerika (OSHA), akazi gasaba ko abantu bafatana uburemere buke n'abandi bakozi, ni ko gafite akamaro.
Ingamba z'ibanze zo kwirinda kwandura zisabwa ahantu hose ho gukorera zirimo gukaraba intoki kenshi no mu buryo bwuzuye, gushishikariza abakozi kuguma mu rugo iyo barwaye, gukurikiza imyitwarire yo gusonza no gusonza harimo no guhisha umunwa n'uruhu iyo basinze no gusonza, gutanga imyenda y'impapuro n'ibisanduku by'isuku, kwitegura gukora kure cyangwa gutegura amasaha y'akazi hakoreshejwe uburyo bufatika niba ari ngombwa, guhagarika abakozi gukoresha ibikoresho n'ibikoresho by'abandi, no gukomeza gukora isuku no gusukura bisanzwe mu gace k'akazi.
Gushakisha abantu bashobora kwandura vuba no kubirinda ni intambwe ikomeye mu kurinda abakozi, abakiriya, abashyitsi n'abandi mu kazi.
