Ingirabuzima fatizo ya angiotensin 2 (ACE2) ifitanye isano n'urufatiro rw'ibinyabuzima byo mu mahaha, mu mishipa, mu mutima, mu bwonko ndetse no mu mara.
Ingingo ya angiotensin 2 itera ingufu za angiotensin 2 (ACE) igabanya ingano ya angiotensin 2 no kongera ingano ya angiotensin (1-7); ikayihindura umuti ugaragaza icyizere mu kuvura indwara z'umutima n'amaraso.
Urubanza rw'umuntu rw'iyo ndwara rukunze kwitwa hACE2.
Ingirabuzima fatizo ya angiotensin 2 ni ingirabuzima fatizo irimo zinc, iri ku gice cy'ingirabuzima fatizo n'ibindi bice by'ingirabuzima fatizo.
Ingirabuzimafatizo ihindura angioutensin 2 irimo urugero rwa peptide M2 ifite umutwe wa amine, n'urutonde rwa coelectrocarboxyline ugizwe n'igice cy'amaraso ya amine.
Ingirabuzima fatizo ya angiotensin 2 ni poroteyine y'uruhu rw'umubiri igenda iyongereraho yo mu bwoko bwa 1, ifite ingirabuzima fatizo zikora ku butaka bw'ingirabuzima fatizo z'ibihaha n'izindi ndwara.
Igice cyo hanze cy'ingirabuzimafatizo gihindura ingyutensiyo 2 kiva mu ngirabuzimafatizo gicibwa n'ingirabuzimafatizo yitwa shidaz, bigatuma poroteyine ihita icika mu maraso hanyuma igasohoka mu munyu.
Ingirabuzima fatizo ya angiotensin 2 iboneka mu bice byinshi by'umubiri: ihura n'uruhu rw'ingirabuzima fatizo z'ubwoko 2 mu mahaha, mu ngirabuzima fatizo z'amaraso, mu ngirabuzima fatizo z'amaraso n'amaraso, ndetse no mu ngirabuzima fatizo z'imitsi y'amaraso z'inkingo z'amaraso mu bice byinshi.
ADN ya RIBO igenewe guhindura ingingo ya angiotensin 2 iboneka mu bwonko, mu gice cyo hasi cy'urugo, mu gice cyo hasi cy'ubwonko.
Igikorwa cy'ingenzi cya ingenzimi ihindura ingenzimi ya angiotensin 2 ni ugukora nk'igihinduranya cya ingenzimi ihindura ingenzimi ya angiotensin.
Ingirabuzima fatizo ya angiotensin ituma ingirabuzima fatizo ya angiotensin 1 ihinduka angiotensin 2 ifata ubwonko bw'amaraso.
Ku rundi ruhande, ingenzimi ihindura angioutensin 2 itandukanya igice cya carboxylic gikubiyemo amino acid phenyle alanin na angioutensin 2 (aspartite-arginine-valine-thyrousin-isoliyosine-hestidine-proline-phenyle alanin) ikayihindura ingioutensin (1-7), (hestidine-aspartite-arginine-valine-thyrousin-isoliyosine-hestidine-proline-phenyle alanin).
Ingirabuzima fatizo ya angiotensin 2 ihinduka indi peptide imwe, ni ukuvuga [des-arginine9] - Bradricine, Apline, Neurotensin, Dinorphine A, na Gerline.
Ingirabuzima fatizo ya angiotensin 2 kandi itegura ingendo z'ibinyabuzima by'ibinyabuzima bitwara amaminosiye SLC6A19, kandi igira uruhare mu ndwara ya Hartnob.
Ingirabuzima fatizo ya angioutensin 2, nk'imiterere ya proteine, ni yo yinjira mu ngirabuzima fatizo ya virusi zimwe na zimwe z'ingori, zirimo virusi ya coronavirusi NL63, SARS-CoV (virus iteza SARS) na SARS-CoV-2 (virus iteza COVID-19).
By'umwihariko, intera y'imiterere ya proteine Spike S1 ya SARS-CoV-2 n'umurongo wa enzymes uhindura ingyutinsine 2 ku gice cy'ingirabuzimafatizo, ituma virusi na enzymes bigira uruhare mu gutwara ingirabuzimafatizo, maze zikajya mu bice by'imbere by'ingirabuzimafatizo.
Iyi gahunda yo gutangiza igiciro cy'ibinyabuzima (S) igomba gukorwa n'ingingo ya protease, serine2, ikoreshwa n'umuntu uyitwara, ikaba ikiri mu igeragezwa nk'umuti ushobora kuvura. Ibi bituma bamwe batekereza ko kugabanya ingano za angiotensin 2 mu ngirabuzimafatizo bishobora gufasha kurwanya ubwandu.
Icyakora, amashyirahamwe menshi y'abahanga n'inzego z'ubuyobozi zigaragaza ko ari byiza gukomeza gukoresha imiti ihindura ingingo za angiotensin, cyangwa ingingo z'ingingo za angiotensin nk'ubuvuzi.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe n'ikigo cya Teloy n'ikigo cya Teloy cyasohotse ku itariki ya 11 Nyakanga 2012 bwagaragaje ko "koresha ingufu z'ingingo z'ubuhinzi z'ingingo z'ibinyabuzima (angitocinine) byari bifitanye isano n'umubare w'abantu bafite ibyago byo kurwara ibihaha ku kigero cya 34% ugereranyije n'abagize itsinda ry'ibanze".
Byongeye kandi, "ibipimo by'ubwandu bw'ibihaha byagabanutse mu barwayi bavurwa n'abandura ingingo z'ibinyabuzima binjiza ingozi ya angiotensin, kandi bari bafite ibyago byinshi byo kurwara ibihaha, cyane cyane abafite ikibazo cy'ihungabana ry'ubwonko cyangwa umutima.
Gukoresha ingufu z'ingingo z'ubudahangarwa za angiotensin byagabanyije umubare w'abapfa bahitanwa n'ihindagurika ry'ibihaha, nubwo ibisubizo byari bike ugereranyije n'ibyago rusange byo guhitanwa n'ihindagurika ry'ibihaha".
Igitekerezo cy'uko ingirabuzima fatizo ya angiotensin 2 (rhACE2) ishobora kuba umuti mushya wo gukira indwara zikomeye z'ibihaha, kigaragazwa ko gifasha mu gutunganya amaraso mu bihaha, ndetse no guhaza umwuka mu ngurube zifite indwara yo guhumeka nabi cyane yatewe na sukari nyinshi z'amavuta.
Ingingo ya 2 y'umwirondoro wa angiotensin igira ubuzima bw'igice cy'amasaha 10, naho igatangira gukora nyuma y'iminota 30, kandi ikomeza gukora (igihe) kugeza amasaha 24.
Hari ibimenyetso byinshi bigaragaza ko ingenzimi ihindura ingenzimi ya angiotensin 2 ishobora kuba umuti uhamye ku bantu bafite intandaro yo kutemera ingenzimi z'ubuhumekero z'ibikomoka ku butsi bw'amaraso (RAS), no ku ndwara ziherekejwe no kuzamuka kw'ingenzimi ya angiotensin 2 mu maraso. Hari ingerageza z'ubuvuzi ziri gukorwa ku ngaruka zo gutera ingenzimi ihindura ingenzimi ya angiotensin 2 mu kuvura indwara yo guhumeka cyane.
Covid-19 ni porogaramu za porogaramu zigenewe ibikoresho by'umwirondoro, zigenewe gufasha gukurikirana abantu banduye mu rwego rwo guhangana n'icyorezo cya Coronavirus 2019-20, bivuze ko ari igikorwa cyo kumenya abantu ("abanduye") bashobora kuba barayobye umuntu ufite ubwandu.
Hari porogaramu nyinshi zashyizweho cyangwa zasabwe n'ubutegetsi bwemewe mu turere tumwe na tumwe n'ubucamanza.
Ibikorwa byinshi byakozwe mu gukora porogaramu zo gukurikirana ibishushanyo.
Abantu benshi bagaragaje impungenge ku bijyanye n'ibanga, cyane cyane ku buryo bikoreshwa mu gukurikirana aho abakoresha porogaramu bari.
Ibindi bintu byoroshye byo kwirinda ubuzima bwite ni ukoresha ibimenyetso bya Bluetooth kugira ngo wandikishe hafi y'umuntu ukoresheje telefoni z'abandi.
Ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple byatangaje ko bishyize hamwe imirimo isaba gukoresha Bluetooth, mu buryo bw'ubucuruzi, mu buryo bw'ikoranabuhanga bwa Android na iOS.
Mu Bushinwa, leta y'Ubushinwa ifatanyije na Alipay, yashyize hanze porogaramu yemerera abaturage kureba niba bahanganye n'abantu banduye COVID-19.
Ni porogaramu ikoreshwa n'abantu mu mijyi irenga 200 yo mu Bushinwa. Muri Singapore, abantu bakoresha porogaramu yitwa TraceTogether.
Ishyirahamwe ry'ubumenyi mu by'ikoranabuhanga ryo mu karere ka Macedonia ryashyizeho porogaramu yo kuyishyira ku mugaragaro, ikaba igiye gushyikirizwa leta.
Minisiteri y'itumanaho n'ikoranabuhanga ikorana n'iyi Minisiteri y'Ubuzima, ni yo yatangije porogaramu.
Ku itariki ya 14 Mata 2020, porogaramu yari ikiri kugenzura ko Apple yemera Google Play Store na App Store.
Ku itariki ya 12 Mata, guverinoma yatangaje ko porogaramu yo gukurikirana abanduye yari mu iterambere ryateye imbere, ishobora kuba iboneka mu byumweru bike.
Australia na New Zealand byombi birimo gutekereza gukora porogaramu zishingiye kuri TraceTogether yatangijwe na Singapore, kimwe na BlueTris.Uturusiya bwatangije porogaramu ikoresha ibidukikije by'abarwayi abaganga basanze banduye COVID-19 baturutse i Moscow, igamije kugenzura ko batava mu rugo.
Ross Anderson, umwarimu wigisha iby'umutekano muri Kaminuza ya Cambridge, yavuze ibibazo byinshi by'ikoranabuhanga bishobora gukorerwa ku mihanda ikoreshwa n'ibikoresho, harimo ko hari ibintu by'ibinyoma byemeza ko ari byiza kandi ko hari igihe usanga nta cyo bitwaye iyo porogaramu zikoreshwa n'abantu bake gusa.
Kugira ngo Apple ihangane n'impungenge z'uko porogaramu za Coronavirus zizakwirakwira, Apple yashyizeho imipaka ku bwoko bw'imiryango ishobora kongeramo porogaramu zayo zifitanye isano na Coronavirusi mu bubiko bwayo bw'imikorere; ibi byashyizweho ku miryango " yemewe " cyangwa indi miryango myiza.
Google na Amazon byashyizeho amategeko nk'ayo.
Abashyigikiye ubuzima bwite bagaragaje impungenge ku ngaruka zo kugenzura abantu benshi ziterwa no gukoresha porogaramu za Coronavirus, cyane cyane ku bijyanye n'uko imikorere y'ubushakashatsi ikenewe mu guhangana n'icyorezo cya Coronavirus izashira igihe cyose iterabwoba rizashira.
Amnesty International n'indi miryango isaga 100 yashyize ahagaragara itangazo ryasabye ko ibi bikorwa by'ubugenzuzi byahagarikwa.
Nanone, imiryango yatangaje ibintu umunani byasabwaga n'ubutegetsi:
Gukurikirana byagombye kuba "biremewe n'amategeko, bikenewe kandi bihuje n'amategeko";
Amasaha yo gukurikirana no kugenzura agomba kuba arimo ingingo zigena igihe cyo guhagarika;
Gukoresha amakuru byagombye kuba biri ku rwego rw'ikoranabuhanga gusa;
Umutekano w'amakuru n'ibanga ry'abafite amakuru bigomba kurindwa kandi bikagaragazwa ko birindwa bishingiye ku bimenyetso;
Kwirinda guhura n'abantu benshi no kubashyigikira mu buryo bw'igitangaza;
Gutanga amakuru ku bantu bo hanze byagombye gushyirwaho n'amategeko;
Ibikoresho by'uburinzi ku ihohoterwa n'uburenganzira bw'abaturage bigomba gushyirwaho kugira ngo bikemure ihohoterwa;
"Kugira uruhare rukomeye" ku "bafite inyungu bose babishoboye", harimo impuguke mu by'ubuzima n'imitwe ihari. Chaos Computer Club (CCC) y'u Budage n'Ikinyamakuru Reporter ohne Grenzen (RSF) na byo byasohoye urutonde rw'ibyo byemezwa.
Gahunda ya Google/Apple igamije guhangana n'ikibazo cy'urwego rw'ubugenzuzi bukomeje mu gukuraho uburyo bwo gukurikirana mu bikoresho bikoresha igihe bikenewe.
Ibihugu bimwe na bimwe byakoresheje urubuga rwo gukurikirana aho gukoresha porogaramu, bituma buri wese adakenera gukuramo porogaramu kandi bikamufasha kwirinda gukurikirana.
Muri Israel, abayobozi bashyize kuri tracking hashingiwe ku mbuga.
Ariko rero, uburyo bwo gukoresha imbuga nkoranyambaga bushobora kugera ku makuru y'ibanze y'urubuga, bugira ibibazo bikomeye by'umwirondoro.
Icyakora, si seriveri zose zifite seriveri z'ibanze zikeneye kubona amakuru y'imyanya bwite; aho hashyizweho uburyo bwinshi bwo kubungabunga ubuzima bwite bukoresha seriveri z'ibanze gusa ku bufatanye hagati y'abantu (reba igice gikurikira hasi).
Muri Koreya y'Epfo, abayobozi bakoresheje uburyo butari bushingiye ku porogaramu kugira ngo bakore ibikorwa byo gukurikirana abajura.
Aho gukoresha porogaramu yihariye, sisitemu ikorakoranya amakuru yo gukurikirana iturutse ku masoko atandukanye, harimo amakuru yo gukurikirana ibikoresho bya telefoni zigendanwa n'amakuru y'ibicuruzwa by'amakarita, kandi ikashyiraho ayo makuru yo kohereza ubutumwa bw'ibimenyetso ku bantu bashobora kuba banduye.
Uretse gukoresha aya makuru mu kuburira abantu bashobora kuba barayobye, leta nayo yashyize amakuru y'imyanya ku mugaragaro, ibyo ikaba yarabyemeye kubera impinduka zikomeye mu mategeko y'ibanga ry'amakuru nyuma y'icyorezo cya Coronavirus cyateje indwara yo mu mutwe yo mu Burasirazuba bwo Hagati.
Aya makuru aboneka ku mugaragaro binyuze mu porogaramu zitandukanye no ku mbuga za interineti. Ibihugu, harimo n'u Budage, byarebye gukoresha sisitemu zishinzwe umutekano ndetse n'izirinda ubuzima bwite.
Tariki ya 6 Mata 2020, amakuru y'ibyo ntaboneka.
Ikoranabuhanga ririmo gukingira ubuzima bwite rigendera ku ihame ryuzuye kandi ryuzuye, rifashishijwe ibitabo bikomeye by'ubushakashatsi byanditswe nibura mu mwaka wa 2013. Ku itariki ya 7 Mata 2020, amatsinda arenga icumi y'impuguke yakoreye ku buryo bwo kugera ku mahitamo y'ibanga, urugero nka Bluetooth ifite ingufu nke (BLE) yo kwandika hafi y'umukoresha ku tundi telefoni ngendanwa.
Icyakora, BEPB-PT yari gahunda yo guhuza irimo uburyo bw'ibanze n'ibanze, aho kuba porotoko imwe. Porotoko z'ibanze z'ibanze zirimo ukurikirana uburyo bw'ibanze bw'ibanze bw'ibanze (DB-PBT/DB-3T), imibare y'itumanaho y'agateganyo (TCN, yari izwi nka nimero z'ibyabaye mu guhura, CEN), porotoko z'ibanze, uburyo bwo gukurikirana ibinyoma binyuze mu bikoresho by'ikoranabuhanga (BACT) n'ibindi.
Muri izo protocole, amakuru y'ibimenyetso ntabwo ava mu gikoresho, kandi ibikorwa byose byo guhura biba ku gikoresho.
Itsinda ry'abikorera mu kigo cya MIT Media Lab ryakoze ku buryo SafePaths, ari uburyo bwo gukoresha ikoranabuhanga ryo kubungabunga ubuzima bwite mu gihe bakusanya amakuru y'imyanya cyangwa mu nzira z'amabarabara, bakayakoresha mu gukurikirana ikwirakwira rya COVID-19.
Ubushakashatsi bwakozwe ku bushakashatsi bwakozwe mu cyegeranyo "Ubushotoranyi bw'ibikoresho: Kurinda ubuzima bwite mu gihe cy'icyorezo" cyasohotse muri Werurwe 2020. Ikigo cya SafeTrace cya Enigma MPC, ikigo gishinzwe iterambere ry'ikoranabuhanga rihuza n'ibanga ry'ibanga cyabanje gushingwa na MIT Media Lab, ni ikindi gikorwa nk'icyo.
SafeTrace ikoresha ikoranabuhanga ry'ibikoresho byiteguye kugira ngo abashobora gusangira amakuru y'imyanya n'ubuzima bw'ingenzi n'abandi basanzwe n'abandi bayobozi batiriwe barangiza ubuzima bwite bw'amakuru.
Ku itariki ya 5 Mata 2020, hashyizweho itsinda ry'abantu bashyiraho gahunda yo gukurikirana imibare y'abantu bakorana ku isi yose, bashyiraho uburyo bwo gukurikirana abantu ku isi yose, bagamije kugabanya itandukaniro no gutuma ikoranabuhanga ry'ikoranabuhanga rikoreshwa ku isi hose, bikaba ari byo by'ingenzi kugira ngo rikoreshwe cyane.
Ku itariki ya 9 Mata 2020, guverinoma ya Singapore yatangaje ko yahisemo gushyiraho protokol ya Blue Tris ikoreshwa na porogaramu ya Leta y'igihugu, ikaba ari isoko ry'urubuga rufunguye.
Ku itariki ya 10 Mata 2020, Google na Apple, ibigo bibiri bigenzura uburyo bwo gukoresha Android na iOS, byatangaje gahunda yo gukurikirana abakora amakosa; aho byavuze ko bizakomeza ubuzima bwite bishingiye ku guhuriza hamwe ikoranabuhanga rya Bluetooth rifite imbaraga nke n'isanduku ikomeza ubuzima bwite.
Nanone basohoye urutonde rw'ikoranabuhanga rikomeye rikoreshwa muri sisitemu.
Apple na Google bavuga ko intego ari ugushyiraho gahunda mu byiciro bitatu:
Gushyiraho ibikoresho byo guha ubutegetsi ubushobozi bwo gukora porogaramu za leta zigenga ubuzima bwite zo gukurikirana virusi ya Corona
Iyi mikorere ihurijwe mu buryo butaziguye muri Android na iOS nkuko Google na Apple biteganya gukemura ibibazo byo gukoresha no kugenzura bikomeje binyuze mu gukwirakwiza sisitemu mbere na mbere binyuze mu kuvugurura sisitemu ya OS hanyuma nyuma yo kuzikuraho mu buryo bumwe ubwo iterabwoba rirangira.
